text: Antoine Costa (born 23 October 1884, date of death unknown) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics and the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:Year of death missing Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sidi Bel Abbès
